column2:
'Dataset'
'If this is the first jo, it may take up to 20 minutes for your pipeline to finish'
'running. The default compute settings have a minimum node size of 0, which'
'means that the designer must allocate resources after eing idle. Repeated'
'pipeline jos will take less time since the compute resources are already allocated.'
'Additionally, the designer uses cached results for each component to further'
'improve efficiency.'
'View scored laels'
'In the jo detail page, you can check the pipeline jo status, results and logs.'
